{
 "_comment": "Evidence catalog - need-signals per artifact, consumed by scripts/scan-evidence.js. Signal kinds: packages (exact NuGet/npm IDs; a trailing '.' or '/' marks a prefix - matched against PackageReference Include= and package.json deps ONLY; a Directory.Packages.props PackageVersion pin alone is never usage under central package management), files (path basenames), csprojContent / content (regex with a required display label - the lint enforces it, and that every key names a real artifact). Curation bar: only unambiguous signals - a signal that fires on unrelated projects is worse than no entry. No entries for hub/router skills, the always-baseline, stack-detected artifacts, or process skills with no artifact trace.",
